OL,3,CLabour to drop #28 billion-a-year
OL,4,Cgreen spending pledge
OL,6,FLabour will abandon its policy of
OL,7,Fspending #28 billion a year on
OL,8,Fenvironmental projects in a major U-
OL,9,Fturn following months of uncertainty
OL,10,Fabout the pledge.
OL,12,FAn announcement on the party's
OL,13,Fflagship green prosperity plan is due
OL,14,Fto be made on Thursday.
OL,16,FSir Keir Starmer is expected to
OL,17,Fconfirm that the pledge is being
OL,18,Fscaled back due to changes in the
OL,19,Feconomic landscape since it was first
OL,20,Funveiled in 2021.
