OL,6,FBut earlier this week, Sir Keir said
OL,7,Fthe money was "desperately needed" for
OL,8,Fthe party's key mission to achieve
OL,9,Fclean power by 2030.
OL,11,FThe Conservatives have also seized on
OL,12,Fthe figure as a key attack line in the
OL,13,Frun-up to an election this year,
OL,14,Fclaiming Labour would ultimately have
OL,15,Fto raise taxes to meet the "unfunded
OL,16,Fspending spree".
