OL,6,FLabour has pointed to recent economic
OL,7,Fturmoil under the Tories, including
OL,8,Fthe turbulence caused by Liz Truss'
OL,9,Fmini-budget in 2022, when accused of
OL,10,Fwatering down its flagship
OL,11,Fenvironmental pledge.
